      "content": "\"wanting everything to end\"... that's exactly what i mean. like, why is it so wrong to just want out? everything is just noise and people being cruel. if things never actually change, then isn't wanting it to end just the only logical way to get some peace? it feels like the only real way to actually escape the loop.",
